            <subsection name="Integrate into maven JSF 1.2">
                To use the package now, you'll have to add another repository to your pom
                <pre>
                    &lt;repositories&gt;
                    ...
                    &lt;repository&gt;
                    &lt;id&gt;org.springframework.security.taglibs.facelets&lt;/id&gt;
                    &lt;url&gt;http://spring-security-facelets-taglib.googlecode.com/svn/repo/&lt;/url&gt;

                    &lt;/repository&gt;
                    ...

                    &lt;/repositories&gt;

                    &lt;dependencies&gt;
                    ....
                    &lt;dependency&gt;
                    &lt;groupId&gt;

                    org.springframework.security
                    &lt;groupId&gt;
                    &lt;artifactId&gt;facelets-taglib&lt;/artifactId&gt;
                    &lt;version&gt;0.1&lt;/version&gt;
                    &lt;/dependency&gt;

                    ....
                    &lt;/dependencies&gt;
                </pre>
            </subsection>

