            <subsection name="Example">
                Just configure your spring-security app the normal way, add
                <pre>
                    xmlns:sec="http://www.springframework.org/security/facelets/tags"
                </pre>
                to the &lt;html&gt;-tag of your .xhtml file... ah I'm too lazy to type this all in,
                just look at the
                <a href="./sec_example.xhtml.txt">Spring-Security + Facelets Example</a>
            </subsection>

